---
// ProblemSection - Pain points highlighting OTA dependency issues
---

<section class="problem-section" id="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <!-- Section header -->
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>
          You Built a Beautiful Hotel.{" "}
          <span class="highlight">Now Booking.com Owns Your Guests.</span>
        </h2>
        <p>
          For years, OTAs promised visibility. In return, they took your margins,
          your guest data, and your independence. Sound familiar?
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pain points grid -->
      <div class="pain-points-grid">
        <div class="pain-point">
          <div class="icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="12" x2="12" y1="2" y2="22"/>
              <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>You pay 15-30% per booking just to fill your rooms</h3>
          <p>Every room sold through an OTA costs you a significant chunk of your revenueâ€”money that should be going toward improving your property.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pain-point">
          <div class="icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
              <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>You have no relationship with guests</h3>
          <p>They're Booking.com's customers, not yours. You can't market to them, build loyalty, or encourage direct repeat bookings.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pain-point">
          <div class="icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="22 17 13.5 8.5 8.5 13.5 2 7"/>
              <polyline points="16 17 22 17 22 11"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>You can't raise prices without OTAs undercutting you</h3>
          <p>Rate parity agreements and OTA algorithms make it nearly impossible to control your own pricing strategy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pain-point">
          <div class="icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect width="18" height="11" x="3" y="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>You're trapped: turn off OTAs, and bookings disappear</h3>
          <p>After years of dependency, your direct booking infrastructure is underdeveloped and can't fill the gap.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Emotional closer -->
      <p class="closer">
        "The worst part? You know there's a better way. You just haven't found it yet."
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: hsl(var(--card));
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .problem-section {
      padding: 8rem 0;
    }
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 56rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif, Georgia, serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.875rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: hsl(var(--foreground));
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .section-header .highlight {
    color: hsl(var(--terracotta));
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: hsl(var(--muted-foreground));
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .pain-points-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .pain-points-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .pain-point {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: hsl(var(--background));
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid hsl(var(--border));
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .pain-point {
      padding: 2rem;
    }
  }

  .pain-point:hover {
    border-color: hsl(var(--terracotta) / 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px hsl(var(--foreground) / 0.08);
  }

  .icon-wrapper {
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    background: hsl(var(--terracotta) / 0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .pain-point:hover .icon-wrapper {
    background: hsl(var(--terracotta) / 0.2);
  }

  .icon-wrapper svg {
    width: 1.5rem;
    height: 1.5rem;
    color: hsl(var(--terracotta));
  }

  .pain-point h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif, Georgia, serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: hsl(var(--foreground));
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .pain-point p {
    color: hsl(var(--muted-foreground));
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .closer {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: hsl(var(--muted-foreground));
    margin-top: 3rem;
    font-style: italic;
    font-family: var(--font-serif, Georgia, serif);
  }
</style>
